Thank you for your continued support over the last couple of years in making Lineage Journey a reality. Please donate to help us continue season 2 and film the last 12 episodes. You can do this through a number of ways.

1. Visiting our website www.lineagejourney.com/donate
2. Donating via PayPal. paypal.me/LineageJourneyDonate
3. Visiting outpostcenters.org/donate select Ministry: OCI Headquarters and Need: Lineage

You may also mail a check to:
Outpost Centers International
5132 Layton Lane
Apison, TN 37302

The check should be made payable to "Outpost Centers International" with a memo that indicates "OCI's work at Lineage."

Support Lineage Journey:
 Paypal: http://bit.ly/2V4jp8r
